  "description": "Meta-monitoring for your Prometheus scrape pipeline: which targets are down, how long scrapes take, and how many samples each target returns. When a dashboard shows \"No data\", this is the board that tells you whether the exporter died, the scrape timed out, or the target simply stopped being discovered.",
